{
  "texts": [
    "D. Limitations and Future WorkWhile the research presents a compelling case for the integration of deep learning and symbolic reasoning, it is not without limitations.",
    "The scope of the current study was confined to benchmark tasks, which, although diverse, do not encapsulate the full spectrum of real-world scenarios.",
    "Future research should explore the application of the hybrid model in dynamically changing environments that mirror reallife complexities.",
    "Additionally, the continuous evolution of language and the emergence of new linguistic constructs present ongoing challenges that necessitate adaptive learning capabilities within the model.",
    "E. Advancing AI ResearchThe study's findings contribute to the broader discourse on advancing AI research."
  ]
}